<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6b3b43ca-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s512"><num value="512">§ 512.</num><heading> Obstruction of navigation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No bridge shall at any time unreasonably obstruct the free navigation of any navigable waters of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6b3b43cb-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/act/1940-06-21/ch409/s2">June 21, 1940, ch. 409, § 2</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/54/498">54 Stat. 498</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
